These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, aquamarine, coral, turquise
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, coach, freelancer, security-guard
4 different games are played: go, chess, billiard, poker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, swimming, baseball, golf
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, spanish, italian, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, quad-bike, train
 1. the brazilian is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 2. the analyst is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing billiard is the spanish##1
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 8. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the freelancer is the person who likes turquise##1
10. the person driving the boat is the person playing chess##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
12. the security-guard is the person who likes aquamarine##1
13. the analyst is in an even position##4
14. the security-guard is the person who's sport is swimming##1
15. the person playing go is the person who likes aquamarine##1
16. the analyst is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
17. the coach is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |       4        |
| Color         | turquise    | grey      | coral | aquamarine        |
| Job           | freelancer | analyst     | coach     | security-guard |
| Game   | chess   | billiard | poker   | go         |
| Sport   | volleyball  | golf        | baseball   | swimming            |
| Nationality           | russian       | spanish  | brazilian    | italian         |
| Transport     | boat       | jet-ski     | train     | quad-bike      |

