.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, aconite, begonia, azalea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana, ritmeester, cain
City: edinburgh, prague, paris, london
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, backgammon, chess
 1. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is the cain-smoker##1
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person traveling to prague##1
 6. the havana-smoker is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 9. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing chess##1
10. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who growsazalea##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
12. the person who growslily is the person playing chess##1
13. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person traveling to london is the person who growsazalea##1
15. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
16. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
17. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
18. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice      | cola         | lemonade | soy-milk    |
| Hobby         | camping    | card-games   | writing  | board-games |
| Flower   | azalea        | begonia | lily   | aconite      |
| Cigar   | havana | ritmeester         | vegafina  | cain      |
| City           | london      | edinburgh         | paris   | prague  |
| Game     | snooker  | backgammon   | chess    | whist     |

